  <!-- Non-bonded interactions for molecule A (PVCN_decamer).  Each entry follows the
       pattern shown in the VOTCA hexane tutorial, specifying the two interacting
       bead types, a radius range and grid spacing, and an <inverse> block with
       the target distribution, update schedule and the name of the table to use
       during CG simulation【368157324134565†L29-L53】.  The "NB_*" names are
       arbitrary identifiers used consistently throughout the workflow. -->

  <!-- Intramolecular pairs inside MOLA (PVCN_decamer) -->
